verbose_text: Transfection of miR-155 inhibitors up-regulated expressions of Rheb and mTOR compared with the model and miR-155 mimics group, while introducing Rheb siRNA into miR-155 inhibitors significantly suppressed the expression of Rheb and mTOR compared to those in the miR-155 inhibitors group (P < 0.05, XREF_FIG, XREF_TABLE).
